data.description:
Walk in and experience true modern farmhouse living in this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Port Orange. Elegance meets comfort as you step into an open-concept living space adorned with rustic accents and contemporary finishes. The gourmet kitchen boasts newer appliances, ample counterspace, and a farmhouse sink, making culinary endeavors a joy. A unique highlight is the inviting Florida room that seamlessly extends your living space, perfect for tranquil mornings or vibrant gatherings. The master suite offers a serene retreat with an en-suite bathroom featuring modern fixtures and a luxurious walk-in shower. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms share a second sleek bathroom. Don't miss your chance to make this home yours and start the next chapter of your life in this welcoming and beautiful space.

All information not guaranteed, Buyer must take own measurements and do their due diligence.
